This directory contains anscillary subroutines that may be
helpful for some applications such as template I/O routines for
input CRM profiles and math routines to convert different
meteorological parameters.

The following is the list of files stored in this directory. 

##################### FILE LIST #######################

-------------- Fortran source codes -------------------

- README-plugins (this file)
	ASCII document to describe the content of this directory.
- rd_CRM_CReSS.f90
	rd_CRM_CReSS: a template of "rd_CRM" for the Cloud Resolving
        Storm Simulator (CReSS).
- def_file_list_CReSS.f90
        def_file_list_CReSS: a template of "def_file_list" for the Cloud 
        Resolving Storm Simulator (CReSS).
- pt2p.f90
        pt2p: calculates air temperature [K] from potential temperature
- q2Wg.f90
        q2Wg: calculates rho*q [g/m3] from mixing ratio (q)
- q2Wkg.f90
        q2Wkg: calculates rho*q [kg/m3] from mixing ratio (q)
- qv2rh.f90
        qv2rh: calculates relative humidity [%] from water vapor mixing ratio
- pwvsat.f90
        pwvsat: calculates saturation water vapor pressure [hPa]

